sort of sweeping burn it down just doesn't work because you wind up building on
rubble. You don't move into a structure that you can clean up and straighten

27:20.780 --> 27:34.300
out. You've got ashes. And I think really those two things were what the book
was all about. The science fictional aspect of that book was the Tisser. Did the

27:34.300 --> 27:50.140
Tisser idea come first and then the story follow? Yes, it did. In fact, the
whole book came from the section titled, What the Inlement, that itself came

